            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesar<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="2"/>divi Nerva<supplied reason="lost">e <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>Nervae Traia<supplied reason="lost">no</supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anico</ex></expan> Daci<lb break="no" n="5"/>co pontifici <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>tribunic</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>XII <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> VI co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>devictis Dacis <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>Foroclaud</abbr><ex>ienses</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>publ</abbr><ex>ice</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Since we&amp;apos;re not sure whether Trajan renewed his tribunicia potestas in December or in January, the date of the inscription could be 107-108 or 108-109.</p>
            </div>
